reviews.author_name: Isus este calea adevarul si viata
reviews.text: Staff members at the front desk are friendly and helpful. Lots of parking space plus extra area for parking. You can lock up your bicycles and charge your electric car in the car park. Right near bus stops and taxi company. The only thing I would say is that it needs more seats while waiting for the train.
The atmosphere of Witham is calm

Staff members at the front desk are friendly and helpful. Lots of parking space plus extra area for parking. You can lock up your bicycles and charge your electric car in the car park. Right near bus stops and taxi company. The only thing I would say is that it needs more seats while waiting for the train.
Lovely provincial railway station. Functional.. What more can you want ?.

Toilets and Waiting rooms locked at 10pm even though passengers have to catch trains timetabled for 11.45pm. It is not run for the comfort or benefit of the passengers. The lights are all on even though the doors are firmly locked. People should be afforded basic amenities. No thought has been given to people with medical problems who need these facilities.
